Suzanne Ridgeway https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Suzanne_Ridgeway 0 Suzanne Ridgeway (January 27, 1918 – May 6, 1996) was an American film actress who appeared in approximately 115 films between 1933 and 1959. She was most often credited as Suzanne Ridgway. Other billings included Suzy Marquette and Susan Ridgway.
